parameters.name: 陵辱系Hシーン【ベースが主役2】

parameters: \n<Riolauno>"It's you. Have you found the woman?"

\n<Deorc>"That's the thing... It's no good. There's no sign of her
anywhere."

\n<Deorc>"We've got men outside the village too, so she shouldn't
have slipped by... It's like she's a ghost."

\n<Riolauno>"...The request was for the sister's capture and the woman's
death."

\n<Deorc>"I know that. She's definitely in the village... Looks like
we have no choice but to 'burn' her out."

\n<Deorc>"Shut up. If you don't close that mouth, I'll really set it
on fire."
\n<Thief>"Heh heh. Just be quiet and behave."

\n<Deorc>"To think someone has a taste for such a tiny sister... Your
client has some interesting preferences. Who exactly made
this request?"

\n<Riolauno>"...Well, clients come in all types. It's better for your
health not to pry too deeply."

\n<Riolauno>"You abduct the sister, and you kill the woman. I just want
that 'fact.' You don't need to think about anything else."

\n<Deorc>"Oh, scary. But I'm not interested in that. You give us the
job, we do the work. As long as we get paid, nothing else
matters."
\n<Deorc>"Let's make a good deal out of this, right? Mr. Riolauno?"
\n<Deorc>"What? What's all this noise about? Shut up!"

\n<Thief>"The Imperial Army... Soldiers from the Valam Empire are
here in the village!"

\n<Deorc>"...Huh? Don't joke around with me. We haven't even been
here half a day yet. There's no way the Imperial Army could
have arrived so quickly."
\n<Deorc>"Stop messing around and find the woman! Otherwise--"

\n<Thief c>"Deorc, sir! The Imperial Army! The soldiers from the Empire
are here!"

\n<Deorc>"Are you serious...? Seriously! You guys aren't messing with
me, are you!?"
\n<Thief>"It's true! The Imperial Army has surrounded the village!"

\n<Deorc>"How could this happen... Damn it! Someone must have
betrayed us... Otherwise, there's no way the Imperial Army
would be here so soon!"
\n<Thief a>"What should we do, Deorc sir?"

\n<Deorc>"What should we do? We fight! You lot drive back the
Imperial Army!!"
\n<Deorc>"Damn it...! Who would have thought it'd come to this...!"
\n<Riolauno>"Hey, where do you think you're going?"

\n<Riolauno>"Don't panic, wait for now. If we move carelessly, we'll be
playing right into the Imperial Army's hands. Haste makes
waste."

\n<Deorc>"What are you so calm about! I don't want to be dragged down
by some smug bastard like you!"

\n<Deorc>"You guys come too! Don't just leave a woman like that
behind!"
\n<Riolauno>"...Can't be helped. I'll take her with me."
